  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d03bc636d4f22964e964f316abda6d60, type: 3}
  m_Name: Story 10
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  chapter: 10
  title: The Final Trial
  story: 'After fixing your spacecraft it crashes again on a volcanic planet, your
    spacecraft is damaged. Only the hot-air balloon module remains attached to your
    vehicle, giving you a way to navigate the hazardous terrain.


    To survive,
    you must complete two challenges. First, collect the key scattered across the
    volcanic map to unlock the repair house. Second, reach 500 altitude by carefully
    manipulating the heat in the balloon. Increasing heat allows you to rise, while
    reducing heat lets you descend, using thermodynamics to stay safe.


    Mastering
    both collecting the key and controlling altitude tests your skill and understanding
    of heat and gas mechanics.


    By completing these tasks, you reach the repair
    station, fix your vehicle, and prepare to return home, triumphant after your
    adventure in ATLAS'
